    "details": "A Secunia Advisory reports:\n\n> Secunia Research has discovered a vulnerability in Opera, which can be\n> exploited by malicious people to conduct cross-site scripting attacks\n> against users.\n>\n> The vulnerability is caused due to input not being sanitised, when\n> Opera generates a temporary page for displaying a redirection when\n> \\\"Automatic redirection\\\" is disabled (not default setting).\n",
